AXA Styleguide!

How to use it

the components are split in 3 categories:

  • Atoms: Which are the essential build blocks
  • Molecules: Which more complex elements and that contains some atoms
  • Organisms: Usually they are final component for a entire section. For example the header is be one. They are ususally composed of more molecules, other organisms and atoms

Filter them:
